title: Maple 12 for Mac (Use this one)
description:
Well, hope this works...thanks for being patient

Again, let me know whether this works

This, as the file name and title imply, is a copy of Maplesoft's Maple 12 I lifted from my schools computers because nobody else uploaded a copy yet. Cleverly, I used the license.dat file from one of the many Windows copies online and off I was, ready to computer the area of a sombrero or find a function that closely resembles a Hershey kiss. 

It works for me.

I made the zip file with stuffit.

So, here's the instructions to install since it isn't an actual install file and I forgot to include a text file.

Copy the 'Maple 12' folder to you applications folder.

Copy the 'Maple.frameworks' folder to hard drive whatever it's called/Library/Frameworks

The cracked license file is already in the right folder (inside Maple.frameworks). 


Also, I'm gonna do my best to stay online as long as I can...no sooner than 10 people who uploaded. My campus blocks p2p so if you don't seed, then it's your damn fault
